

install the node.js

initialized and setup the project using *npm init*

installed the dependencies like *mongoose*

setup the webserver contents using *express* and *body-parser*

created the database config js file with module.exports

add database configuration on server.js file

create the route file *movie.routes.js*

now, created controller named movie.controller.js

//For setup postgres
npm i express pg

install postgres

install pgAdmin

create server, database and tables


